c: 24
v: 23
t: "'iina aladhin yqdhfwn balzna alefyfat alghafilat almuminat allaati lm yukhtir dhlk bqlwbhn, mtrwdwn min rahmat allah fi aldunya walakhrt, walahum eadhab eazim fi nar jhnm. wafi hadhih alayat dalil ealaa kafar min sbb، 'aw aitaham zawjat min zwjat alnabiu salaa allah ealayh wasalam bsw'"